System Modules

1. User Management

Handles registration, authentication, and profile management for users, inventory staff, and administrators.

2. Product Management

Manages product details such as name, code, category, price, quantity, and description.

3. Supplier Management

Stores and manages supplier information, contact details, and supply history.

4. Stock Management

Tracks stock availability, updates inventory levels, and monitors low-stock items in real time.

5. Purchase Management

Records product purchases, increases stock quantity, and maintains purchase history.

6. Sales Management

Records sales transactions, decreases stock quantity, and maintains sales history.

7. Reporting and Analytics

Generates inventory reports, stock summaries, purchase reports, and sales analytics for better decision-making.

